 Justification:
 The FY2027 budget request prioritizes procurement of systems or enablers in accordance with the Marine Corps prioritized H-1 Mid-Life Modernization strategy. Improvements to safety of flight, maintenance,
 obsolescence (diminishing manufacturing sources/material shortages), aircrew situational awareness and readiness degrader items yield a more interoperable and survivable H-1 force. Systems improved on H-1
 aircraft leverage common avionics architectures to mitigate modification costs, procurement costs, and reduce fielding timelines while attacking the highest readiness degraders and improve readiness rates.




