 Justification:
 The FY 2027 funding request is for modifications to a group of trainer aircraft systems which includes the US Navy Test Pilot School (USNTPS) aircraft, the TH-73A, and the T-54.

 OSIP 006-07 FY 2027 TH-57 SAFETY UPGRADE is archived.

 OSIP 005-04 FY 2027 T44 AVIONICS OBSOLESCENCE is archived.

 OSIP 015-16 FY 2027 request continues the T-38 Wing Upgrade Program, Talon Repair, Improvement, and Modification (TRIM).

 OSIP 006-23 FY 2027 request addresses correction of deficiencies modifications for the TH-73A program.

 OSIP 011-26 FY 2027 request addresses Avionics Obsolescence modifications for the T-54 program.

 OSIP 012-26 FY 2027 request addresses safety issues on the TH-73A platform.

