 Justification:
 The FY 2027 request provides funding to procure aircraft modifications to include Electronic Countermeasures (ECM), Safety, Reliability, Readiness and Obsolescence Issues and Communication Navigation
 Surveillance System (CNS) Air Traffic Management (ATM) requirements such as Block Upgrade (BU) 8.1 for the KC-130J program. FY 2027 increases Block 7.0/8.1 Kits, increases STAR-XIII Mission Computer
 procurement, initiates EGI-M Integration NRE, initiates Comm Suite Modernization NRE, increases Cargo Winch B-Kits, initiates Electronic Circuit Breaker Unit NRE, and initiates Wireless ICS NRE. FY 2027
 also initiates USN LAIRCM JABS Kit procurement, Control Display Unit (CDU) Kit procurement, NP2000 installs and increases C/KC-130T GPS Kit procurements, High Frequency Radio B-Kits, SATCOM B-Kits,
 Weather Radar kit procurement, Center Wing Box Kit procurement, NP2000 Kit procurement, CDU NRE/Test, Weather Radar NRE, Weather Radar installs.




