 Justification:
 The Next Generation Jammer Mid-Band (NGJ-MB) OSIP 002-19 support procurement of NGJ-MB shipsets and associated support. FY 2027 request includes the procurement of 10 shipsets (2 pods per
 shipset) of AN/ALQ-249 Next Generation Jammer Mid-Band (NGJ-MB) for Lot 7 Production, Support Equipment (SE), Integrated Logistics Support (ILS), Other Support and Data. FY 2027 SE request includes
 Organizational-Level (O-Level) and Intermediate-Level (I-Level) Common and Peculiar Support Equipment for accelerated squadron stand-up, as well as Depot-Level (D-Level) Support Equipment. ILS includes
 Interim Contractor Support (ICS) and Fleet Service Representative (FSR) support from the prime contractor to support initial Fleet squadrons and deployments. Other Support is production engineering support
 required to execute the NGJ-MB production program from multiple field activities. FY 2027 Data request includes funds to acquire data packages related to obsolescence, and organic capability for Depot level
 and Intermediate level repair of system components.

 The Next Generation Jammer Low Band (NGJ-LB) OSIP 001-28 supports the procurement of AN/ALQ-266 NGJ-LB pod production, support equipment, integrated logistics support, data and other support
 required to produce, deliver and establish operational, intermediate and depot level organic repair capability the NGJ-LB capability.




